<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hu">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Skyhigh AI | Vezérlőpult</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body { background-color: #050505; color: white; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
        .tech-card { background: #0c0c0e; border: 1px solid #1f1f22; border-radius: 16px; }
        .glass-btn { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); border: 1px solid #27272a; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; transition: 0.2s; color: #a1a1aa; }
        .glass-btn:hover { background: #a855f7; border-color: #a855f7; color: white; }
        .modal { display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.95); z-index: 100; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 20px; backdrop-blur: 10px; }
        .modal.active { display: flex; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #27272a; border-radius: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="p-4 md:p-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto">

    <header class="flex justify-between items-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-8">
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-black italic tracking-tighter">Skyhigh<span class="text-purple-500">.AI</span></h1>
            <nav class="hidden md:flex gap-3">
                <button onclick="openModal('techModal')" class="glass-btn">Technológia</button>
                <button onclick="openModal('stratModal')" class="glass-btn">Stratégia</button>
            </nav>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
            <div class="text-right hidden sm:block">
                <p class="text-[9px] text-zinc-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-[2px]">Rendszer Állapot</p>
                <p class="text-xs font-bold <%= user.hasLicense ? 'text-green-500' : 'text-purple-500' %>">
                    <%= user.hasLicense ? 'AKTÍV LICENC' : 'DEMO MÓD' %>
                </p>
            </div>
            <a href="/logout" class="bg-zinc-900 p-2 px-4 rounded-lg text-zinc-400 hover:text-white transition text-[10px] font-bold uppercase">Kilépés</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
        
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 tech-card flex flex-col h-[650px] shadow-2xl border-white/5">
            <div class="p-4 border-b border-zinc-800/50 flex justify-between items-center bg-zinc-900/20">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Skyhigh Kvantum-Asszisztens</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="chatBox" class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-6 space-y-6">
                <div class="flex justify-start">
                    <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 text-zinc-300 p-4 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none text-sm border border-zinc-800 max-w-[80%]">
                        <p>Üdvözlöm, Operátor. A rendszer készen áll az elemzésre. Milyen tőkével dolgozunk a mai napon?</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <form id="chatForm" class="p-4 bg-zinc-900/30 border-t border-zinc-800 flex gap-2">
                <input type="text" id="userInput" placeholder="Írjon az asszisztensnek..." class="w-full bg-black/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm focus:border-purple-500 outline-none transition">
                <button type="submit" class="bg-purple-600 w-14 rounded-xl hover:bg-purple-500 transition flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-purple-900/20">
                    <i class="fas fa-paper-plane text-sm"></i>
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-4">
            
            <% if (!user.hasLicense) { %>
                <div class="tech-card p-6 border-purple-500/20 bg-purple-500/5">
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold mb-2">Licenc Szükséges</h3>
                    <p class="text-xs text-zinc-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">A Master Tippek és a teljes bankroll menedzsment csak előfizetőknek érhető el.</p>
                    <a href="/fizetes" class="block w-full bg-white text-black py-4 rounded-xl font-black uppercase text-[10px] text-center tracking-widest hover:bg-purple-600 hover:text-white transition-all">
                        Licenc Aktiválása (20.000 Ft)
                    </a>
                </div>
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="tech-card p-6 border-green-500/20">
                    <h3 class="text-[10px] font-black text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Napi Quantum Tipp</h3>
                    <% if (dailyTip) { %>
                        <div class="bg-black/60 p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 mb-3">
                            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-white mb-1 uppercase"><%= dailyTip.match %></p>
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mt-2">
                                <span class="text-purple-400 text-xs font-bold"><%= dailyTip.prediction %></span>
                                <span class="text-green-500 font-bold">ODDS: <%= dailyTip.odds %></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-[10px] text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed italic"><%= dailyTip.reasoning %></p>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-600 italic text-center py-4">Elemzés folyamatban...</p>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            <% } %>

            <div class="tech-card p-6 border-zinc-800">
                <h3 class="text-[10px] font-black text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Rendszer Paraméterek</h3>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-[11px]">
                    <div class="flex justify-between"><span class="text-zinc-500">Modell:</span><span class="text-zinc-300">Skyhigh-v4 (Pro)</span></div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between"><span class="text-zinc-500">Tőke:</span><span class="text-zinc-300"><%= user.startingCapital %> Ft</span></div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between"><span class="text-zinc-500">Stratégia:</span><span class="text-green-500 font-bold">Fix 30 Napos</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="techModal" class="modal">
        <div class="bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 p-10 rounded-3xl max-w-xl w-full">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase mb-6 text-purple-500">Kvantum Technológia</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">A Skyhigh AI nem tippeket ad, hanem valószínűségszámítást végez. A GPT-4 motorunk minden reggel 15.000+ adatpontot elemez (formamutatók, xG, sérülések és piaci mozgások), hogy megtalálja az értéket.</p>
            <button onclick="closeModal('techModal')" class="w-full py-4 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition">Bezárás</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="stratModal" class="modal">
        <div class="bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 p-10 rounded-3xl max-w-xl w-full">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase mb-6 text-green-500">Fix Profit Stratégia</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-400 text-sm mb-6">
                <p>1. <strong>Szigorú tőkekezelés:</strong> Soha ne tegyél fel többet a bankod 5%-ánál!</p>
                <p>2. <strong>Ciklus szemlélet:</strong> A profitot 30 napos egységekben mérjük.</p>
                <p>3. <strong>Érzelemmentes fogadás:</strong> A robot utasításait követni kell, függetlenül az előző nap eredményétől.</p>
            </div>
            <button onclick="closeModal('stratModal')" class="w-full py-4 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition">Értettem</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function openModal(id) { document.getElementById(id).classList.add('active'); }
        function closeModal(id) { document.getElementById(id).classList.remove('active'); }

        const chatBox = document.getElementById('chatBox');
        const chatForm = document.getElementById('chatForm');
        
        chatForm.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
            e.preventDefault();
            const text = document.getElementById('userInput').value;
            if(!text) return;
            document.getElementById('userInput').value = '';
            chatBox.innerHTML += `<div class="flex justify-end"><div class="bg-purple-600 text-white p-3 px-5 rounded-2xl rounded-tr-none text-sm shadow-xl font-medium">${text}</div></div>`;
            chatBox.scrollTop = chatBox.scrollHeight;

            const res = await fetch('/api/chat', {
                method: 'POST',
                headers: {'Content-Type': 'application/json'},
                body: JSON.stringify({ message: text })
            });
            const data = await res.json();
            chatBox.innerHTML += `<div class="flex justify-start"><div class="bg-zinc-900 text-zinc-300 p-4 px-6 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none text-sm border border-zinc-800 leading-relaxed shadow-lg"><strong class="text-purple-500 block text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 italic">Rendszerüzenet</strong>${data.reply}</div></div>`;
            chatBox.scrollTop = chatBox.scrollHeight;
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>